name: CF6 Power - Kelowna Flightcraft DC-10-30F [C-GKFT] Taxi and Spool Up at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Follow me on Flickr: https://www.flickr.com/photos/dude8472productions/

Flashback Friday! I was feeling nostalgic about the DC-10 and found this clip from January of this year. The video features C-GKFT taxiing close up, and then spooling up on 35L. The sound is one of the best I've caught, IMO. Anyway, I hope you enjoy this short video!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
